      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0600P0-03763'>
        <a name='S5LV0600P0_19990510_GCR_190'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-sally-hamwee' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0600P0_19990510_GCR_190' title='Link to this speech by Ms Sally Hamwee' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
